A tutorail by Mitch Koko
Learn to build basic login page ui in flutter , you will learn some of the regulary used widgets in flutter
#
In this Flutter tutorial, 
the focus is on coding the UI for a login screen. 
The tutorial covers creating a blank scaffold, 
adding images for Apple and Google logos, styling text fields, 
creating a sign-in button,
and adding options for alternative sign-in methods. 
The tutorial sets the stage for implementing authentication methods in future videos.


